Package: duckbotos-session-picker
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: python3, systemctl,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: DuckBotOS session picker — choose Hermes / OpenClaw / Hybrid at boot
 Provides a beautiful web-based session picker UI served on port 8080.
 This is what Both/Hybrid mode users see when they boot DuckBotOS —
 a dark-themed UI with cards for Hermes, OpenClaw, and Hybrid GNOME
 workstation modes. Keyboard navigable (1/2/3 to select, Enter to launch).
 .
 The picker runs as a systemd service (duckbotos-session-picker.service)
 and writes the selected mode to /etc/duckbotos/kiosk-mode so the kiosk
 knows which agent dashboard URL to load.